Attorney Seong Yudeok
from Law Group Hyungmin.

00:10:20.621 --> 00:10:21.663
What?

00:10:23.123 --> 00:10:25.209
First, have a seat.

00:10:26.877 --> 00:10:27.920
What's going on?

00:10:28.837 --> 00:10:31.215
Did you submit
the wrong power of attorney forms?

