Are you still…

00:19:12.819 --> 00:19:14.363
Going to argue self-defense?

00:19:19.910 --> 00:19:20.911
About that…

00:19:21.703 --> 00:19:24.915
I'm thinking about
what would be best for you.

00:19:26.166 --> 00:19:27.835
What would you like to do?

